It was easy to understand, guided step by step. I like the way the instructor explained everything, a little bit fast but changing the speed of the videos helped me because my first language is not English. Canva have changed the organization/location of some of its tools compared to the ones shown in the videos, but it just took me a few minutes to find them. Overall, I like the guided project.

What a fun and efficient way to learn how to navigate Canva. I have used Canva for projects, but I really did not know what I was doing. so, what should have been a simple task took me forever. I'm thrilled because I just made a video, which came out, even if I say so myself, pretty awesome.
